# mallowsSequence

- _mallowsSequence(n)_

Answer the first _n_ terms of Mallows’ integer sequence.

Mallows’ sequence,
OEIS [A005229](http://oeis.org/A005229):

```
>>> 20.mallowsSequence
[
	1  1  2  3  3  4  5  6  6  7
	7  8  9 10 10 11 12 12 13 14
]
```

Mallows’ sequence,
OEIS [A005229](http://oeis.org/A005229):

~~~spl svg=A oeis=A005229
99.mallowsSequence.linePlot
~~~

